<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/sep/15/">&#x27a0;</a> September 15, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="apple_breaks_the_ipod_ui_a_lit" >

        
        <a name="002034"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=302244">Apple breaks the iPod UI a little more</a></h4>

        

        <p>Number of button presses required to see/change the rating of a track on the iPod nano:  Three, Four or Five, depending on whether you have Lyrics and Cover Art attached to the track.  Hey Apple!  Remember &#8220;consistency&#8221;?</p>

